# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3D viewer — recorded trajectories
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The CURATED scenario files in viz/web/trajectories/ (the demo + the named
# scenarios + manifest.json) are COMMITTED — they ship with the repo and are
# published to GitHub Pages, so they are intentionally NOT ignored here.
#
# Real recorded rollouts (e.g. exported from a JAX run via viz/recorder.py) can
# be large; drop them in viz/web/recordings/ instead, which is ignored.
viz/web/recordings/

